    "display_name": "Build a Playlist",
    "long_instructions": "## Build a Playlist\r\n\r\n**Before You Start:**\r\n\r\nMake sure you have filled in the **K** and **W** columns of your KWL chart for this task.\r\n\r\n**Do:**\r\n\r\nAsk AI to create a themed playlist for studying, a party, or a mood.\r\n\r\n**Try:**\r\n\r\nAsk for different genres, decades, or vibes. Try naming one song and asking for 5 more like it.\r\n\r\n**Check:**\r\n\r\nDo the songs fit your theme? Are they real, and would you actually listen to them?\r\n\r\n**After You Try It:**\r\n\r\n1. Fill in the **L** column of your KWL chart\r\n2. Press **Continue** to return to the task menu\r\n\r\n",
